replies.body:
Hi paff!
As an ARAM fan i liked the ban phase and the rest of the new features! But riot stated it was experimental! I believe they will add the features once again based on the feedback they get and there could've been some bugs that they want to fix, but something tells me we haven't seen the last of those features.

 {{sticker:sg-ahri-2}}

My account is ARAM only champs, for the most part.

Bans were definitely needed, especially at 2.5k+ MMR. But if you plan on leaving the poke nerf in, you _**HAVE**_ to address certain tanks/bruisers as well. They are just as (if not, even more) overpowered as the long ranged pokers.

